 last 2 movies separately. This movie is still phenomenal, and holds up jus=
t as well today if not better. It's incredible to see how this film has mat=
ured and become social commentary that's just as relevant now as it ever wa=
s. The Wachowskis have gone on to do some great films and some not so great=
, but hoping that the new M4TRIX (see what I did there) does to post-2020, =
what this film did for the early 2000s.<br>
